file.name: openapi-spec.yaml
file.content:
openapi: "3.0.0"
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: Falcon Openapi Demo
  license:
    name: MIT
paths:
  /foo:
    get:
      summary: Do foo things
      operationId: controllers.foo.Foo.on_get
      parameters:
        - name: limit
          in: query
          required: false
          schema:
            type: string
      responses:
        200:
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/Foo"
    post:
      summary: Do foo things
      x-falcon:
        module: controllers.foo
        class: Foo
      parameters:
        - name: limit
          in: query
          required: false
          schema:
            type: string
      responses:
        200:
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/Foo"
    put:
      summary: Do foo things
      x-falcon:
        module: controllers.foo
        class: Foo
      parameters:
        - name: limit
          in: query
          required: false
          schema:
            type: string
      responses:
        200:
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/Foo"
components:
  schemas:
    Foo:
      properties:
        bar:
          type: string
        baz:
          type: string
